{"tid":706492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"墨西哥的真王牌23號","createTime":"2018-06-18T02:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T02:55:17.000Z","uid":191019,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"14eb36945ba3afa7c7e3da04ffc64b966d325157","tid":706492,"uid":191019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:55:17.000Z","msg":"利申：日韓中毒，最近先睇波的跟風狗<br />\n<br />\n巴打有睇琴晚場波都知墨西哥22號仔入左粒。<br />\n但都睇到其實佢地兩個，即係22同23號都有相當多機會進攻，甚至有3,4次單刀的機會。德國對墨西哥左翼的防守弱已經係事實。<br />\n22號把握到<br />\n23號把握唔到<br />\n叫個右腳仔打左翼係正常的，起唔到腳都正常的。<br />\n我要做既野，就係期待你下次的左腳抽射。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/105400_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F105400_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff6609b3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}